## Third-party Licenses and Attributions

This project uses the following third-party libraries and datasets:

### Model Dependencies
- **OpenAI Whisper**: Licensed under MIT License
  - Repository: https://github.com/openai/whisper
  - Used for base ASR models (whisper-large-v2, whisper-large-v3-turbo)

- **Hugging Face Transformers**: Licensed under Apache 2.0 License  
  - Repository: https://github.com/huggingface/transformers
  - Used for model loading and inference infrastructure

- **PEFT (Parameter-Efficient Fine-Tuning)**: Licensed under Apache 2.0 License
  - Repository: https://github.com/huggingface/peft
  - Used for LoRA (Low-Rank Adaptation) fine-tuning

### Dataset Attribution
- **HAT-Vol2 Dataset**: Hakka ASR Training Corpus
  - Provided by the Formosa Speech Recognition Challenge organizers
  - Usage restricted to FSR-2025 competition participants
  - Contains Taiwanese Hakka speech data (Dapu and Zhao'an dialects)

- **FSR-2025-Hakka-evaluation**: Competition Evaluation Dataset
  - Provided by National Yang Ming Chiao Tung University (NYCU)
  - Usage restricted to FSR-2025 competition participants

### Competition Framework
- **Formosa Speech Recognition Challenge 2025**: Organized by NYCU
  - Challenge website: https://sites.google.com/nycu.edu.tw/fsw/home/challenge-2025
  - Competition rules and dataset usage governed by FSR-2025 terms

### Python Libraries
- **PyTorch**: Licensed under BSD-3-Clause License
- **torchaudio**: Licensed under BSD-3-Clause License  
- **NumPy**: Licensed under BSD License
- **tqdm**: Licensed under MIT License
- **opencc-python-reimplemented**: Licensed under Apache 2.0 License

