```bibtex
@misc{fsr2025-hakka-asr,
  title={FSR-2025 Hakka ASR Challenge: Complete Implementation for Hanzi and Pinyin Recognition},
  author={Level-Up Team},
  year={2025},
  publisher={GitHub},
  journal={GitHub Repository},
  howpublished={\url{https://github.com/your-username/FSR-Challenge-2025}}
}
```

## Data Usage Restrictions

- The HAT-Vol2 and FSR-2025-Hakka-evaluation datasets are provided solely for the FSR-2025 competition
- Commercial use of the datasets is prohibited without explicit permission from the dataset creators
- Redistribution of the original datasets is not permitted
- This code can be used independently with other Hakka ASR datasets under the MIT license terms

## Competition Compliance

This implementation complies with the FSR-2025 competition rules:
- No manual labeling of test/evaluation data
- Only automated speech recognition techniques used
- No external language models beyond those specified in competition guidelines
- All training data limited to provided HAT-Vol2 corpus

---

For questions about licensing or dataset usage, please contact the original dataset providers or competition organizers.